5","tid":1233444,"uid":24265,"like":67,"dislike":652,"score":-585,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"樓主都on9 當呢度大陸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8717d0104a7e4d4232c085f43595413578c73b02","tid":1233444,"uid":28109,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"咪啦，仲黎俾啲掌聲自己呀？"},{"pid":"98a9ba7c9a7ca0be37eaa3099490053c0fdbdea1","tid":1233444,"uid":225531,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:33.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n有去發夢嘅年輕人，可能你就快18歲、啱18歲，又或者係過歲數但未登記成為選民，可唔可以用少少時間填吓選民登記，收保皇黨香港走狗嘅皮，投番啲正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（你有兩票，一票自己住嗰區，另一票係超級區議會，好好善用佢）<br />\n<br />\n地方選區：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=GC&amp;applicationId=GC1&amp;module=1&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2Fmain.jsp%3Frt%3DGC%26applicationId%3DGC1%26module%3D1%26language%3Dzh%26country%3DHK&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=fcaeb1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=GC&amp;applicationId=GC1&amp;module=1&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK</a><br />\n<br />\n功能組別&mdash; 區議會（第二）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=FC&amp;applicationId=FC41&amp;module=41&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2Fmain.jsp%3Frt%3DFC%26applicationId%3DFC41%26module%3D41%26language%3Dzh%26country%3DHK&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=62719134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/main.jsp?rt=FC&amp;applicationId=FC41&amp;module=41&amp;language=zh&amp;country=HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n屋企人阻住你發夢嘅香港人，可唔可以幫下文宣組手足，簽吓聯署、整圖、share post咁，多一個係一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】正式開火！第一批信已發出！我地香港人要幫政府官員、保皇黨取消外國護照！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第二輪炮火！行動升級！除咗取消港共外國護照，我地正式開辟聯合國人道罪行戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217474</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第三波強攻！不撤不散！林鄭月娥、速龍指揮、江敏強，我地要你地生生世世被困大灣區！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226922</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n投柒訴CCTVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c50ad069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n「TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實」<br />\n<br />\n時間12-17/6/2019 任何一日，任何一段新聞報導，6:00am 得、6:30pm 又得<br />\n81台，83台有得<br />\n「呃我老母屌你老母」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c50ad069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n<br />\n好叻叫醒裝睡的人嘅香港人，可唔可以再幫幫手炮轟佢地，用理據，一巴巴摑醒仍在裝睡嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（對唔住我口才唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交俾咁多位巴絲freestyle）"},{"pid":"d9460a4a0d018bc2b89cf92514bdf08971b7c185","tid":1233444,"uid":158977,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c24e08b280e3cb545e78e213287e51c9c0fd37b5","tid":1233444,"uid":24265,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"quote":{"pid":"57d11de2c2c17504deec989d77e6e4feb33223de","tid":1233444,"uid":155853,"like":243,"dislike":5,"score":238,"quote":{"pid":"94bef3e90e89c78f3deb63475af3f8759171a865","tid":1233444,"uid":24265,"like":67,"dislike":652,"score":-585,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"樓主都on9 當呢度大陸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no